{"id":"api/router/upgrade/setUpLocationSync","title":"setUpLocationSync","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/router\", \"name\": \"@angular/router\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/router/upgrade\", \"name\": \"@angular/router/upgrade\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/router/upgrade/setUpLocationSync\", \"name\": \"setUpLocationSync\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/router\">@angular/router</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/router/upgrade\">@angular/router/upgrade</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/router/upgrade/src/upgrade.ts?message=docs(router)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L54-L117\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/router/upgrade/src/upgrade.ts#L54-L117\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"setuplocationsync\">setUpLocationSync<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/upgrade/setUpLocationSync#setuplocationsync\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">設定 location 更改監聽器以觸發 <code>history.pushState</code>。解決 <code>onPopState</code> 不會觸發\n<code>history.pushState</code> 的問題。必須在呼叫 <code>UpgradeModule.bootstrap</code> <em>之後</em>呼叫。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Sets up a location change listener to trigger <code>history.pushState</code>.\nWorks around the problem that <code>onPopState</code> does not trigger <code>history.pushState</code>.\nMust be called <em>after</em> calling <code>UpgradeModule.bootstrap</code>.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/router/upgrade/setUpLocationSync\" class=\"code-anchor\">setUpLocationSync</a></span>(ngUpgrade: <a href=\"api/upgrade/static/UpgradeModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">UpgradeModule</a>, urlType: \"path\" | \"hash\" = 'path')</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"引數\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>ngUpgrade</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/upgrade/static/UpgradeModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">UpgradeModule</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">升級 NgModule。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The upgrade NgModule.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>urlType</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>\"path\" | \"hash\"</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">location 策略。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">可選值。預設值為 <code>'path'</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The location strategy.</p>\n\n\n        \n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/upgrade/setUpLocationSync#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/common/HashLocationStrategy\" class=\"code-anchor\">HashLocationStrategy</a></code></p></li>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/common/PathLocationStrategy\" class=\"code-anchor\">PathLocationStrategy</a></code></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/router/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common/HashLocationStrategy\n - api/common/PathLocationStrategy\n - api/router\n - api/router/upgrade\n - api/router/upgrade/setUpLocationSync#see-also\n - api/router/upgrade/setUpLocationSync#setuplocationsync\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeModule\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/router/upgrade/src/upgrade.ts?message=docs(router)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L54-L117\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/router/upgrade/src/upgrade.ts#L54-L117\n-->"}